Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.33,0:00:11.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得没什么回忆是要被忘记的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.04,0:00:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.65,0:00:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紫吴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.79,0:00:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于5月1日的事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.62,0:00:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下午我能出个门吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.23,0:00:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.91,0:00:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天我也有事不在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.35,0:00:36.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.21,0:00:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和咲她们出门？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.95,0:00:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.86,0:00:41.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我母亲的忌日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.86,0:00:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去扫墓
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.03,0:00:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦 已经是一周年的忌日了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.34,0:00:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.38,0:00:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有什么需要特别做的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.11,0:00:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 没办法一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.00,0:00:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 没这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.98,0:00:56.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.14,0:00:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.58,0:00:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想去扫一扫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.47,0:01:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本田你母亲的墓
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.05,0:01:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.64,0:01:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我妈妈也一定会很高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.89,0:01:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夹 你没什么事的话就跟去扫墓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.49,0:02:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那王子也要来啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.26,0:02:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夹呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.23,0:02:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.40,0:02:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他没说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.25,0:02:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.53,0:02:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉今日子会很喜欢夹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.17,0:02:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定会使劲逗他的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.56,0:03:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橘子橘子 我要吃了你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.26,0:03:06.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后把终于怒发冲冠的夹…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.04,0:03:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用能把他脖子折了的力道抱住
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.35,0:03:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个不太好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.78,0:03:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各种意义上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.32,0:03:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经有一年了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.29,0:03:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你母亲去世
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.66,0:03:25.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是总觉得现在还会突然出现一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.69,0:03:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说着『抱歉抱歉』一脸笑眯眯的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.97,0:03:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.02,0:03:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得 让气氛变得悲伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.15,0:03:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.14,0:03:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今日子就是这么厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.38,0:03:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像『还七的赤蝶』这个传说一样不灭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.70,0:03:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小透
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.94,0:03:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快让我藏起来 藏起来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.43,0:03:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红叶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.60,0:03:53.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在在玩警察抓小偷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.84,0:03:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是小偷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.63,0:03:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红叶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.48,0:03:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你躲起来也是没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.12,0:03:59.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小透 今天要去打工吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.15,0:04:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.72,0:04:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 小偷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.48,0:04:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 我发现红叶了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.65,0:04:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红叶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.86,0:04:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前面 看前面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.47,0:04:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 他爸爸还是妈妈是德国人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.43,0:04:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.75,0:04:21.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草摩家的人不太提自己的双亲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.26,0:04:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明在父母面前都没有这么笑过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.69,0:04:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 小透
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.62,0:04:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下红叶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.27,0:04:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}红叶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.57,0:04:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前面 看前面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.55,0:04:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小透 很努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.07,0:04:42.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在她能这么笑之前
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.02,0:04:47.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定骂过无数次想要放弃的自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.24,0:04:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于我来说 如果小透死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.09,0:04:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的可以在一年之后露出笑容吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.50,0:05:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许会希望干脆连相遇都忘了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.70,0:05:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小透很努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.27,0:05:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这个搬走工作就结束了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.82,0:05:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有那边休息室的垃圾箱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.62,0:05:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我拿过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.07,0:05:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 可是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.51,0:05:22.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开心就好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.45,0:05:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.96,0:05:29.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.47,0:05:30.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说了没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.05,0:05:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这个 今天也是由希来接你？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.24,0:05:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.12,0:05:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔夹也来接一下你不是挺好？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.28,0:05:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是死要面子活受罪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.59,0:05:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 红叶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.34,0:05:41.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.33,0:05:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红叶你父母哪一边是德国人？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.78,0:05:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mutti
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.00,0:05:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 Mutti是？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.09,0:05:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.77,0:05:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦 是妈妈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.80,0:05:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有照片
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.26,0:06:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.37,0:06:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红叶很像妈妈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.22,0:06:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.53,0:06:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 爸爸是草摩家的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.75,0:06:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸和妈妈是大学时候相遇然后结婚的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.67,0:06:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸真是竟然能泡到这么漂亮的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.74,0:06:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后然后
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.85,0:06:21.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还有个妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.62,0:06:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫做小桃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.09,0:06:24.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和妈妈一模一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.70,0:06:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 红叶居然还有妹妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.94,0:06:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.82,0:06:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在小学2年级
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.93,0:06:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 但是小桃不是十二生肖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.11,0:06:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后超爱撒娇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.94,0:06:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像小鸡仔一样屁颠屁颠跟在妈妈后面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.44,0:06:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是日语不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.29,0:06:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跌跌撞撞的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.90,0:06:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}感觉很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.36,0:06:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超可爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.59,0:06:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈和小桃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.10,0:06:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本上都会来接爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.50,0:06:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 差不多到时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.75,0:06:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要一起回去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.91,0:06:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.89,0:06:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吃牛排
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.65,0:07:01.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是妈妈不认识我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.88,0:07:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.00,0:07:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红叶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.49,0:07:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是红叶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.25,0:07:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.77,0:07:12.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么晚了还在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.25,0:07:16.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说曹操 曹操就到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.69,0:07:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我朋友在这里打工
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.26,0:07:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以过来玩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.11,0:07:22.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.70,0:07:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这里可不是游乐场啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.17,0:07:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.65,0:07:31.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那这位就是小桃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.63,0:07:35.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是还是红叶比较像妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.78,0:07:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且回去太晚的话 你妈妈会担心的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.04,0:07:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 马上就回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.50,0:07:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 不要绕路啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.05,0:07:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.34,0:07:47.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小桃我们走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.30,0:07:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸等急了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.16,0:07:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清扫辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.00,0:07:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.01,0:07:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 小桃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.18,0:08:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真倒霉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.75,0:08:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真倒霉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.04,0:08:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.28,0:08:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下要去和爸爸道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.47,0:08:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红叶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.07,0:08:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 妈妈不认识我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.32,0:08:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.16,0:08:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消除记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.20,0:08:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈以为我是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.21,0:08:28.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草摩家某人的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.29,0:08:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被妖怪附身的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.86,0:08:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般都会提前两个月
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.45,0:08:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而不是十个月足月产
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.84,0:08:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和喜欢的人相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.28,0:08:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和喜欢的人结婚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.99,0:08:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和喜欢的人生孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.73,0:08:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱着这个孩子的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.70,0:08:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然变成了奇怪的动物幼崽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.57,0:08:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这对于 妈妈来说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.05,0:08:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会是一件多么让人绝望的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.20,0:09:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生出被妖怪附身的孩子的母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.83,0:09:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不就是过分保护
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.48,0:09:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要么就是拒绝承认
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.58,0:09:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本上就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.77,0:09:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的妈妈是拒绝的那种
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.72,0:09:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生理上的拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.53,0:09:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,选择了无视我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.58,0:09:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算这样也很焦躁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.83,0:09:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是歇斯底里的大叫着什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.24,0:09:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在想想 整个都坏掉了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.10,0:09:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像佳菜那样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.74,0:09:40.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红叶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.37,0:09:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈好像不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.05,0:09:50.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也许忘了红叶就能治好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.44,0:09:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道这会让红叶很难受
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.43,0:09:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸会连上妈妈的份
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.26,0:09:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更加更加爱你的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.43,0:10:02.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然红叶也爱着妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.80,0:10:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就帮帮妈妈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.61,0:10:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.80,0:10:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的要选择忘记吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.66,0:10:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不后悔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.36,0:10:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这一辈子最后悔的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.69,0:10:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是 从自己的身体里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.59,0:10:30.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生出了那个动物这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.01,0:10:38.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 我就从妈妈的记忆中消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.02,0:10:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈渐渐变得有精神了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.18,0:10:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个月后就能笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.98,0:10:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.28,0:10:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.51,0:10:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救了妈妈吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.71,0:11:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直 都在一边默默看着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.37,0:11:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从远处一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.75,0:11:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让她不会发现
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.51,0:11:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次见到你的时候 之所以在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.41,0:11:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概也是为了看看妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.15,0:11:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.39,0:11:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.20,0:11:28.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要好好背起回忆活着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.24,0:11:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算 这是悲伤的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.66,0:11:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个回忆只会让我痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.40,0:11:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算这个回忆让我想要忘却
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.21,0:11:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好背负着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.14,0:11:48.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不逃走 努力着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.60,0:11:52.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要肯努力总有一天…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.52,0:11:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天 我会变得不会输给这份回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.97,0:11:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直相信着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.70,0:12:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要 相信着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.20,0:12:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让人想要忘记的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.32,0:12:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得是不存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.57,0:12:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.46,0:12:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以其实我也不想让妈妈忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.16,0:12:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想让她努把力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.57,0:12:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.78,0:12:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只是我的任性
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.51,0:12:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个秘密哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.71,0:12:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.23,0:12:48.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也 我也相信着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.00,0:12:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论什么回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.23,0:12:55.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要相信 都可以放在心中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.24,0:12:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.56,0:13:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去 扫墓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.19,0:13:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了让自己不会认输
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.68,0:13:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.61,0:13:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会越过这些
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.18,0:13:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让它成为记忆中的一页
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.89,0:13:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天气不错真好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.56,0:13:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近天气都不好 我还有点担心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.01,0:13:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许是因为妈妈高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.01,0:13:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为大家都来扫墓了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.65,0:13:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小透
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.87,0:13:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 小鱼 小花
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.85,0:13:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 今天真是扫墓的好日子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.85,0:13:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.73,0:13:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说你那是什么打扮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.70,0:13:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.15,0:13:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然很土是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.88,0:13:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.08,0:14:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鱼 你这该不会是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.77,0:14:02.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特攻服 吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.56,0:14:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 知道不少嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.28,0:14:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是今日子给的正版的赤蝶特攻服
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.08,0:14:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤 赤蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.85,0:14:16.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是妈妈道上混的时候的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.80,0:14:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道上混…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.48,0:14:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人都到齐了 快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.45,0:14:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走路都在飘
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.52,0:14:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是飘的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.09,0:14:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.41,0:14:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺干净的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.13,0:14:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁来过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.29,0:14:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 肯定是爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.82,0:14:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为爷爷知道妈妈喜欢吃什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.34,0:14:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.92,0:14:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.18,0:14:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷是哪边的爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.15,0:14:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是爸爸的爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.42,0:14:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今日子和父母关系很不好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.89,0:14:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爸爸 怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.69,0:14:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感冒拖严重了 就这样…好像是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.73,0:15:00.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候我还小
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.98,0:15:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不太记得了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.11,0:15:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊 所以那时候才那样…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.67,0:15:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈我来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.17,0:15:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.87,0:15:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过爷爷都打扫干净了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.80,0:15:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就没什么可做了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.08,0:15:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲死了 母亲也死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.50,0:15:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.74,0:15:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么还可以 笑得毫无阴霾 如此明媚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.73,0:15:36.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还记得事故当天的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.62,0:15:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上课的时候她被老师叫过去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.36,0:15:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微说了几句话她就冲出了教室
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.31,0:15:48.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个朋友也追在她后面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.24,0:15:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教室里掀起了一阵骚动
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.24,0:15:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.29,0:15:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有身边的人遇到事故了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.89,0:16:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呆呆的想着这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.59,0:16:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实也就只有这个朦胧的印象
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.26,0:16:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本田透 这个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.46,0:16:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.38,0:16:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.08,0:16:15.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.86,0:16:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离那么近
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.19,0:16:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由希
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.67,0:16:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看 很漂亮的花
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.53,0:16:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己居然和她一起笑着 不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.21,0:16:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 咦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.53,0:16:32.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放不好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.45,0:16:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.57,0:16:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王子 把那边支住
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.24,0:16:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.48,0:16:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花岛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.28,0:16:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这…那啥…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.42,0:16:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是能看见 灵魂什么的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.73,0:16:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能看到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.41,0:16:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我完全没有灵视力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.31,0:16:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.54,0:16:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你 电波…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.74,0:16:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电波和灵视力完全是两码事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.34,0:16:59.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别混为一谈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.08,0:17:03.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电波也就是人类的思绪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.73,0:17:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起用耳朵去听
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.08,0:17:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电波更像是直接在脑中回响的语言
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.17,0:17:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要说明
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.69,0:17:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么突然这么问
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.53,0:17:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是突然想到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.67,0:17:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么具体意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.59,0:17:21.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后 活着的人类才是最强的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.34,0:17:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电波也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.05,0:17:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了的人的电波大多很微弱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.33,0:17:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在活人思绪的强度面前
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.76,0:17:33.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会被覆盖掉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.03,0:17:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.50,0:17:42.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在你的电波超级响
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.43,0:17:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会带着如此悔恨的心情站在坟前
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.31,0:17:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混沌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.80,0:18:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夹 小花
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.80,0:18:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.68,0:18:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.34,0:18:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.64,0:18:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.88,0:18:08.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.73,0:18:09.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.89,0:18:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要在坟前掏出便当啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.40,0:18:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.02,0:18:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今日子更喜欢吵吵闹闹的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.29,0:18:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被和尚看到怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.65,0:18:24.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道歉就行了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.49,0:18:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 一般不会这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.06,0:18:28.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之坐下吧 夹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.87,0:18:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你站着我很不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.24,0:18:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.53,0:18:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夹 要吃什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.30,0:18:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随便
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.51,0:18:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.22,0:18:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}给
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.01,0:18:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鱼你们和本田的妈妈关系很好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.04,0:18:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很熟的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.89,0:18:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在认识之前就因为她是个传说所以很憧憬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.86,0:18:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传说？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.86,0:18:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说是赤蝶传说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.83,0:18:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今日子只要骑上摩托
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.79,0:18:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红色尾灯就像蝴蝶飞舞一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.01,0:19:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得那啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.00,0:19:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那三个人的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.82,0:19:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近越来越不错了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.96,0:19:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王子也没有像刺猬一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.53,0:19:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夹也是对小透的事挺照顾的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.76,0:19:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉总有一天会说出喜欢小透这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.69,0:19:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.96,0:19:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不会那么简单就承认小透恋爱了的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.67,0:19:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁家小姑子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.53,0:19:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 这大半是玩笑话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.56,0:19:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一半是来真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.86,0:19:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草摩由希和草摩夹依然是一片混沌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.59,0:19:44.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混乱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.89,0:19:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然无法明确知道形状
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.65,0:19:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被阴暗的思绪支配着内心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.80,0:19:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种东西谁都有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.78,0:19:58.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那两个人相当严重
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.74,0:20:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要那个思绪还存在一天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.84,0:20:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就没有余力去谈恋爱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.71,0:20:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有我要再多说一句
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.39,0:20:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那两个人 对这种事超级迟钝的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.11,0:20:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个小透也一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.35,0:20:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.72,0:20:18.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫名其妙的 发现之后
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.39,0:20:20.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定春天就到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.57,0:20:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.02,0:20:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小透居然要嫁人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.89,0:20:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一这么想 我就想哭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.87,0:20:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也太跳跃了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.95,0:20:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天一天辛苦后的茶真好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.07,0:20:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天扫墓好开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.51,0:20:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.88,0:20:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能把由希和夹介绍给她真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.03,0:20:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 这两个人就是一直照顾我的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.43,0:20:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一天能见到紫吴就更好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.61,0:21:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 我在这个家里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.49,0:21:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和大家每一天都很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.77,0:21:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.11,0:21:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后也请放心的 保佑我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.80,0:21:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.27,0:21:27.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这家伙要睡在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.22,0:21:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 会感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.35,0:21:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.51,0:21:37.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是小孩睡姿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.74,0:21:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.65,0:21:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被风吹走了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.13,0:22:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帽子？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.00,0:22:18.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.90,0:23:52.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样
